===================================================================== 

CFJ 1078 

     "Morendil violated Rule 1729 by voting on Proposal 3640 in the 
      Public Forum." 

====================================================================== 

Judge:       Blob
Judgement:   TRUE

Justices:    elJefe (C), Gen. Chaos (J), Oerjan (pro-S) Decision:

