Injunction by Judge Blob:

By the power invested in me, by Rule 908, I hereby issue an Injunction that
Morendil submit a Formal Apology using the following Proscribed Words:

Insanity, inanity, profanity, calamity, Yosemite, perimetry, gee, I'm, a, tree! 

